<body>
<div type="letter">
  <pb facs="1037812" n="1"/>
<opener><salute>Illustrissimo et Doctissimo Viro
    <lb/><rs type="person">Sebastiano Checotio</rs>
    <lb/><abbr>S. P. D.</abbr> <rs type="person">N. B.</rs></salute></opener>
  <p><lb/>Etsi ex <rs type="letter">responsione</rs> tua, quam <date>nuper</date> accepi, gratum mihi fuerit
    <lb/>intelligere, te non prorsus eam sententiam fovere, quam in pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice><pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>cedente mea <rs type="letter">epistola</rs> mihi refutandam esse <del><gap/></del><add>existima</add>bam; nondum
    <lb/>tamen omnis inter nos dissensus sublatus est: nullam enim ejus
    <lb/>rei, quam demonstrandam esse dicebam, attulisti <rs type="biblio">demonstratio<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nem</rs>. Ne autem <del><gap/></del>denuo versemur
    <lb/>in ignoratione ejus, quod <add>inter nos</add> controversum est, statum qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>stionis sic
    <lb/><lb/>pono: <figure/><!-- BeideFiguren in einem ausschneiden, da sie zusammengehören. --> Sint du<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> Curv<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <formula>BEC</formula>, <formula>bec</formula>, quarum axes <formula>AC</formula>, <formula>ac</formula>, signifi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>cent tempora duorum descensuum integrorum,
    <lb/>absciss<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>libet <formula>AD</formula>, <formula>ad</formula>, tempora descensuum par<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tialium, applicat<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <formula>DE</formula>, <formula>de</formula>, vires in fine temporum
    <lb/><formula>AD</formula>, <formula>ad</formula>, agentes, et applicat<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> prim<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <formula>AB</formula>, <formula>ab</formula>, vires
    <lb/>agentes in principio descensuum; qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>stio est, an
    <lb/>rite <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> te demonstratum sit, quod posita ista
    <lb/>analogia <choice><orig><formula>AB . ab:: AC . ac</formula></orig><reg><formula>AB : ab = AC : ac</formula></reg></choice> figur<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <formula>BECA</formula>, <formula>beca</formula>,
    <lb/>sint similes. Ad hoc quidem demonstrandum nihil ali<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ud dicis, quam <cit type="long"><quote><choice><orig><g ref="#quote">„</g></orig><reg></reg></choice>rectas <formula>AB</formula>, <formula>AC</formula>, coordinatasque ceteras 
        <lb/><choice><orig><g ref="#quote">„</g></orig><reg></reg></choice>non tempora aut vires esse, sed ad ista exprimenda relatione quadam
        <lb/><choice><orig><g ref="#quote">„</g></orig><reg></reg></choice>assumtas, si earum qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>libet cum reliquis ejusdem generis conferatur,
        <lb/><choice><orig><g ref="#quote">„</g></orig><reg></reg></choice>et hinc fieri, ut qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>cunque demum absolut<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> temporum, viriumque
        <lb/><choice><orig><g ref="#quote">„</g></orig><reg></reg></choice>significationes iis affingantur (analoga quadam substitutione) e<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>dem
        <lb/><choice><orig><g ref="#quote">„</g></orig><reg></reg></choice>ips<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> line<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>, modo semel rem confecerint, semper sint proposito satisfa<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/><choice><orig><g ref="#quote">„</g></orig><reg></reg></choice>ctur<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>.</quote></cit> H<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>c verba, pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>terquam quod idem per idem explicant, hunc sen<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>sum mihi habere videbantur, nempe quod quicunque affingatur valor 
  <pb facs="1037813" n="2"/> 
  <lb/>lineis <formula>AB</formula>, <formula>AC</formula>, <abbr>i. e.</abbr> qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>cunque fuerit relatio inter <formula>AB</formula> et <formula>AC</formula>, aut
    <lb/>inter <formula>ab</formula> et <formula>ac</formula>, semper futurum sit <choice><orig><formula>AB.DE\;::\;ab.de</formula></orig><reg><formula>AB:DE=ab:de</formula></reg></choice> si tempora
    <lb/>sumta fuerint in hac ratione  <choice><orig><formula>AC.AD\;::\;ac.ad</formula></orig><reg><formula>AC:AD=ac:ad</formula></reg></choice>. Animadverti autem
    <lb/>ex <rs type="letter">responsione</rs> tua, te propositionem pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>dictam restringere ad
    <lb/>eam conditionem, <del><gap/></del><hi rend="u">si null<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> quantitates con<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>stantes ingrediantur relationem qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> est inter <formula>AB</formula> et <formula>AC</formula></hi> <abbr>h. e.</abbr> si
    <lb/><formula>AB</formula> fuerit ut potestas aliqua ipsius <formula>AC</formula>. Admitto hanc responsionem,
    <lb/>sed addo necesse esse (quo analoga illa tua substitutio fieri possit)
    <lb/>ut null<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> quantitates constantes ingrediantur non solum relatio<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nem qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> est inter <formula>AB</formula> et <formula>AC</formula>, sed et eam qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> est inter reliquas
    <lb/>coordinatas <formula>DE</formula> et <formula>DC</formula>, sive <formula>de</formula> et <formula>dc</formula>. Jam vero quia natura Cur<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>varum <formula>BEC</formula>, <formula>bec</formula>, incognita supponitur, nondum scimus annon
    <lb/>in constructione applicatarum <formula>DE</formula>, <formula>de</formula>, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> dependent <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> rectis <formula>AB</formula>,
    <lb/><formula>AC</formula>, <formula>ab</formula>, <formula>ac</formula> (constantibus pro eodem descensu) et ab abscissis va<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>riabilibus <formula>CD</formula>, <formula>cd</formula>, adhibend<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> sint ali<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> quoque line<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> constan<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tes pro omnibus descensibus, quarum tamen singul<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> ad alias sui
    <lb/>generis referantur. Nam licet in Curva <formula>BEC</formula> <abbr>ex. gr.</abbr> <formula>BA</formula> eodem mo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>do formetur ex <formula>AC</formula>, quo applicata <formula>DE</formula> formatur ex abscissa <formula>DC</formula>,
    <lb/>potest tamen dubium esse, a<choice><orig><g ref="#nn">n̄</g></orig><reg>nn</reg></choice>on <del><gap/></del>termini
    <lb/>illi, quos ingrediuntur quantitates ill<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> constantes, evanescant in
    <lb/><del><gap/></del>expressione applicat<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <formula>AB</formula>, <del><gap/></del>non
    <lb/>autem evanescant in expressione ceterarum applicatarum <formula>DE</formula>.
    <lb/>Tales autem line<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> constantes in constructione Curvarum <formula>BEC</formula>,
    <lb/><formula>bec</formula>, necessario adhiberi debent, nempe ill<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> sint mensur<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
    <lb/>temporum, virium, spatiorum. Fingamus <abbr>ex. gr.</abbr> vim gravitatis
    <lb/>ordinariam et constantem, qualis apud nos est,<del><gap/></del>
    <lb/>repr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sentari per rectam <formula>G</formula>, <figure/> et hanc vim talem esse, ut corpus
    <lb/><del><gap/></del>grave recta
    <lb/>descendens percurrat tempore <formula>T</formula> spatium <formula>S</formula>; ist<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> 
  <pb facs="1037814" n="3"/> 
    <lb/>igitur tres quantitates <formula>G</formula>, <formula>T</formula>, <formula>S</formula>, ingredientur <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>quationem, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> ex<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>primit relationem coordinatarum <formula>DE</formula>, <formula>DC</formula>, <formula>de</formula>, <formula>dc</formula>, in Curvis
    <lb/><formula>BEC</formula>, <formula>bec</formula>, et singul<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> ad alias sui generis referentur, <formula>G</formula> ad <formula>AB</formula>, <add><formula>DE</formula>, <abbr><choice><orig><g ref="#etlig">&amp;</g></orig><reg>et</reg></choice>c.</abbr></add><supplied>,</supplied>
    <lb/><formula>T</formula> ad <formula>AC</formula>, <add><formula>AD</formula>, <abbr><choice><orig><g ref="#etlig">&amp;</g></orig><reg>et</reg></choice>c.</abbr></add> et <formula>S</formula> ad spati<del><gap/></del><add>a percursa.</add> Tuum jam
    <lb/>est demonstrare, quantitates has <del><gap/></del><formula>G</formula>, <formula>T</formula>, <formula>S</formula>, ita in <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>quationem Cur<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>varum <formula>BEC</formula>, <formula>bec</formula> ingredi, ut in nostro casu similitudinem ea<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rundem Curvarum <formula>BEC</formula>, <formula>bec</formula>, non destruant. Tale autem aliquid
    <lb/>in <abbr>artic.</abbr> I<choice><orig><g ref="#ndot">.</g></orig><reg></reg></choice> et II<choice><orig><g ref="#ndot">.</g></orig><reg></reg></choice><!-- ToDo: Kontrollieren ob I et II oder ob 1 et 11. --> <rs type="biblio">investigationis</rs> tu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> demonstratum esse, his atten<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tius consideratis, dubio procul non asseres, sed, ut spero, reperies
    <lb/>haud frustraneam fuisse objectionem meam. Quod attinet ad pro<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>priam meam <rs type="biblio">solutionem</rs>, neque ea mihimet <del><gap/></del>tantopere
    <lb/>arridet, ut aliquas ejus delitias tibi promittere ausim; eamque
    <lb/>tu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>, postquam legitima demonstratione firmata fuerit, liben<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ter postponam. </p> <closer>Vale et in dies, ut coepisti, corroborari perge, me<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>osque tibi placendi conatus boni consule. <dateline>Dabam <rs type="place">Pat.</rs> <abbr>a. d.</abbr> <date when="1719-03-31">31. <abbr>Mart.</abbr> 1719</date>.</dateline></closer>
</div>
